<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>HoangTrungDev - Portfolio & Hub Dự Án</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #0b0f19;
            --card-bg: #131c2e;
            --text-color: #f3f4f6;
            --text-muted: #9ca3af;
            --accent-primary: #6366f1;
            --accent-secondary: #a855f7;
            --cyan-accent: #06b6d4;
            --success-color: #10b981;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-color);
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .brand-logo-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .logo-website {
            height: 90px;
            width: auto;
            object-fit: contain;
            border-radius: 50%;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.3);
        }

        .brand-logo {
            font-size: 2.4rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #38bdf8, #a855f7);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .bct-badge-img {
            height: 42px;
            width: auto;
            margin-top: 5px;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }
        .bct-badge-img:hover { transform: scale(1.05); }

        header p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(400px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }

        .card {
            background-color: var(--card-bg);
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            border-color: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.4);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), 0 8px 10px -6px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1);
        }

        .card-preview-container {
            height: 230px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            background-color: #05070f;
        }

        .card-img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.5s ease;
        }

        .card:hover .card-img { transform: scale(1.03); }

        .card-content {
            padding: 25px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            flex-grow: 1;
        }

        .card-title {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .card-description {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            flex-grow: 1;
        }

        .tags {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .tag {
            background-color: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1);
            color: #a5b4fc;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            border: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2);
        }

        .card-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--accent-primary), var(--accent-secondary));
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
        }
        .card-btn:hover { opacity: 0.9; }

        .interactive-section {
            background-color: var(--card-bg);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 30px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #ffffff;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--cyan-accent);
            padding-left: 10px;
        }

        .contact-channels {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-bottom: 35px;
        }

        .contact-btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, filter 0.2s ease;
        }
        .contact-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            filter: brightness(1.1);
        }

        .btn-zalo { background-color: #0068ff; }
        .btn-facebook { background-color: #1877f2; }

        .form-group { margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        .form-control {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: rgba(11, 15, 25, 0.6);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 12px;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            outline: none;
        }
        .form-control:focus { border-color: var(--accent-primary); }

        .submit-btn {
            background-color: transparent;
            border: 1px solid var(--cyan-accent);
            color: var(--cyan-accent);
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }
        .submit-btn:hover { background-color: var(--cyan-accent); color: #0b0f19; }

        #comment-box {
            margin-top: 15px;
            min-height: 300px;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 60px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            padding-top: 25px;
        }
        .footer-copyright { margin-top: 5px; font-size: 0.85rem; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <div class="brand-logo-container">
                <img src="logo.png" alt="HoangTrungDev Logo" class="logo-website">
                <div class="brand-logo">HoangTrungDev</div>
                <img src="bct.png" alt="Đã Đăng Ký Bộ Công Thương" class="bct-badge-img">
            </div>
            <p>Hệ sinh thái sản phẩm công nghệ & Nền tảng ứng dụng trực tuyến</p>
        </header>

        <div class="grid">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-preview-container">
                    <img src="devstudio-preview.png" alt="DevStudio Preview" class="card-img">
                </div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h2 class="card-title">DevStudio</h2>
                    <p class="card-description">Nền tảng cung cấp giao diện giải pháp số toàn diện phục vụ cấu trúc hệ thống quản trị và tối ưu hóa vận hành doanh nghiệp.</p>
                    <div class="tags">
                        <span class="tag">HTML5</span><span class="tag">CSS3</span><span class="tag">UI/UX</span>
                    </div>
                    <a href="https://m0trix-1.github.io/c05/" target="_blank" class="card-btn">Truy cập dự án</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-preview-container">
                    <img src="techpulse-preview.png" alt="TechPulse Preview" class="card-img">
                </div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h2 class="card-title">TechPulse</h2>
                    <p class="card-description">Chuyên trang thông tin công nghệ cao, cập nhật dòng chảy liên tục của AI Engineering, Tự động hóa và An ninh mạng.</p>
                    <div class="tags">
                        <span class="tag">AI Engineering</span><span class="tag">Cybersecurity</span><span class="tag">Next-Gen</span>
                    </div>
                    <a href="https://m0trix-1.github.io/TechPulse/" target="_blank" class="card-btn">Truy cập dự án</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="interactive-section">
            <h3 class="section-title">Kênh Liên Hệ Trực Tuyến</h3>
            <div class="contact-channels">
                <a href="https://zalo.me/0328509184" target="_blank" class="contact-btn btn-zalo">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-comment-sms"></i> Nhắn tin Zalo (0328509184)
                </a>
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/1DJLMLCBVA/?mibextid=wwXIfr" target="_blank" class="contact-btn btn-facebook">
                    <i class="fa-brands fa-facebook"></i> Kết nối Facebook
                </a>
            </div>

            <h3 class="section-title">Báo Cáo Lỗi Hệ Thống (Nhận qua Email thật)</h3>
            <div class="report-form-container">
                <form action="https://formspree.io/f/YOUR_FORM_ID" method="POST">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>Dự án phát hiện sự cố</label>
                        <select name="Project" class="form-control" style="background-color: #0b0f19;">
                            <option value="DevStudio">DevStudio (c05)</option>
                            <option value="TechPulse">TechPulse</option>
                            <option value="Hub-Main">Trang tổng hợp (HoangTrungDev)</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>Mô tả chi tiết lỗi phát sinh</label>
                        <textarea name="Message" class="form-control" rows="4" placeholder="Nhập nội dung lỗi phát sinh tại đây..." required></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Gửi báo cáo lỗi</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="interactive-section">
            <h3 class="section-title">Bình Luận & Góp Ý Công Khai</h3>
            <div id="comment-box"></div>
        </div>

        <footer>
            <p>&copy; 2026 HoangTrungDev. Tất cả quyền được bảo lưu.</p>
            <div class="footer-copyright">Hệ thống bảo mật & Chống hàng giả mã nguồn đã kích hoạt.</div>
        </footer>
    </div>

    <script>
        var disqus_config = function () {
            this.page.url = window.location.href;  
            this.page.identifier = window.location.pathname; 
        };
        (function() { 
            var d = document, s = d.createElement('script');
            s.src = 'https://hoangtrungdev.disqus.com/embed.js'; 
            s.setAttribute('data-timestamp', +new Date());
            (d.head || d.body).appendChild(s);
        })();
    </script>
</body>
</html>
